'''托马斯·提格'''（{{lang|en|'''Thomas M. Tigue'''}}，{{bd|1945年|8月24日|2016年|2月1日}}），是一名[[宾夕法尼亚州众议院|宾夕法尼亚州众议院]]民主党议员。

== 生平 ==
1964年，毕业于圣约翰高中，后在{{le|宾夕法尼亚州国王学院|King's College (Pennsylvania)}}毕业，1968年获得本科学位<ref name="official">{{cite web|title=Thomas M. Tigue (Democrat) |work=Official Pennsylvania House of Representatives Profile |publisher=Pennsylvania House of Representatives |url=http://www.legis.state.pa.us/cfdocs/legis/home/member_information/house_bio.cfm?districtnumber=118 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060110010657/http://www.legis.state.pa.us/cfdocs/legis/home/member_information/house_bio.cfm?districtnumber=118 |archivedate=2006-01-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。他效力于[[美国海军|美国海军]]，并参加越南战争，获得[[银星勋章|银星勋章]]<ref name=record />。之后他供职于{{le|海兵队予备役|Marine Forces Reserve}}长达27年<ref name=hof />，随后在{{le|玛丽伍德大学|Marywood University}}攻读研究生学位<ref name=drmec>{{cite web| title = Our Team -  Thomas M. Tigue, Managing Director| work = www.drmec.org| publisher = Delaware River Maritime Enterprise Council, Inc| year = 2007| url = http://www.drmec.org/section2008.php?sec=Team2008}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。他担任{{le|宾州东斯特劳斯堡大学|East Stroudsburg University of Pennsylvania}}立法成员及{{le|皮茨顿教区|Pittston Area School District}}委员会成员<ref name=record>{{cite web |first=Paul|last=Kanjorski|authorlink=Paul E. Kanjorski|title = HONORING STATE REPRESENTATIVE THOMAS TIGUE AS HE RETIRES FROM THE PENNSYLVANIA LEGISLATURE AFTER 26 YEARS OF SERVICE |work = [[国会议事录|国会议事录]]| publisher = United States Congress|date = 2007-02-09|url = http://bulk.resource.org/gpo.gov/record/2007/2007_E00308.pdf}}</ref>。

1980年，他首次当选{{le|宾夕法尼亚州众议院第118选区|Pennsylvania House of Representatives, District 118}}议员，进入[[宾夕法尼亚州众议院|宾夕法尼亚州众议院]]。在任期间，他担任退伍军人事务部和应急准备委员会的民主党主席，期间他致力于推动《军人家庭救灾援助计划》（{{lang|en|Military Family Relief Assistance Program}}），旨在对军事人员在军事活动中，其家属能够获得财政支持<ref name=hof>{{cite press release| title = RETIRED LAWMAKER TOM TIGUE NAMED TO MILITARY AND VETERANS AFFAIRS HALL OF FAME| publisher = [[Pennsylvania_Department_of_Military_and_Veterans_Affairs|Pennsylvania Department of Military and Veterans Affairs]]| date = 2007-07-31| url = http://www.milvet.state.pa.us/DMVA/1789.htm| access-date = 2016-02-02| archive-date = 2016-03-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303201758/http://www.milvet.state.pa.us/DMVA/1789.htm| dead-url = no}}</ref>。此外，他也通过立法授权州长能够召集{{le|宾夕法尼亚州国民警卫队|Pennsylvania National Guard}}执行州内紧急任务<ref name=hof />。他在{{le|2006年宾夕法尼亚州众议院选举|Pennsylvania House of Representatives elections, 2006}}之前退休。

2006年12月，他担任特拉华河海企业委员会管理主任<ref name=drmec />。2007年7月，他被邀请进入{{le|宾夕法尼亚州军队和退伍军人事务部|Pennsylvania Department of Military and Veterans Affairs}}名人堂<ref name=hof />。同年他试图进入卢塞恩县委员会，以取代即将退休的托蒂·万德海德<ref name=commissioner />，然而在普通诉讼法庭上，提格却被前任委员长罗斯·塔克以5:4击退<ref name=commissioner>{{cite news| title = Former Commissioner Tucker tapped to finish rest of Vonderheid’s term| work = Citizens Voice| place = Wilkes-Barre, Pennsylvania| publisher = Times-Shamrock Communications Inc| date = June 19, 2007| url = http://citizensvoice.com/site/news.cfm?newsid=18491537&BRD=2259&PAG=461&dept_id=455154&rfi=6| accessdate = 2016-02-02| archive-date = 2011-07-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110718105202/http://citizensvoice.com/site/news.cfm?newsid=18491537&BRD=2259&PAG=461&dept_id=455154&rfi=6| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2016年2月1日，他因肺癌晚期去世<ref>{{cite news|author1=BILL WELLOCK |title=Former lawmaker Tigue dies |url=http://citizensvoice.com/news/former-lawmaker-tigue-dies-1.2002022 |accessdate=2016-02-02 |agency=citizensvoice |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306060529/http://citizensvoice.com/news/former-lawmaker-tigue-dies-1.2002022 |archivedate=2016-03-06 }}</ref>。

